What free scraping can and can't reach on LinkedIn Can reach (logged-off):\
Company page posts when the page is public \'97 often visible Public profile pages with the direct URL \'97 visible but limited LinkedIn Jobs listings \'97 fully visible LinkedIn Articles \'97 mostly indexed and visible Some posts via Google site:linkedin.com/posts search \'97 partial coverage, indexing delay of hours to days Can't reach (or reaches unreliably):\
